ass=m><span class=title>   Evil Eyes?</span><hr size=1> I'd been hunting in HH for faction and when I'm in a group that can't get a descent camp we've been wandering down to the gorge to kill minos - and we thought evil eyes.  They slaughter me every time by charming my pet.  I usually get charmed myself before I can get off a cancel magic.  Anyone have suggestions about hunting these (ie pet strategy) because I'd think the beholder mage would be a fun place to hunt at these levels with a group and it seems very underutilized, thanks. <p><font face="Times new roman" size="5"><b><font 
